Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.79,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:17.73,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地變得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:23.14,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,背後彷彿有你的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:30.09,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,追趕了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:41.20,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我頻頻回頭看著你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:51.30,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,新戀情的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.41,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,是兩人在不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:07.19,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,展開看不見的愛的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.36,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永遠不願分離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.61,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓我只愛你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修的家在那邊是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏是我跟阿修\N上過的幼兒園吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經從那個溜滑梯跌下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引起了不小的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美那時候就跟我同班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來變成不同班\N只有在國中的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩人緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地走在\N前往展望台的坡道上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我們就能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使走完坡道，來到了展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們依然沒有將手分開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們依然沒有將手分開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}#03 兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聽不見心跳聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實它還是噗通噗通的跳著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對我的身體感到好羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想從這世界消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，即使是這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是在談著戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我們還能像這樣\N眺望著這個城鎮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你，還有我們的小鬼\N一起出門去吃大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我一定會很想\N讓他們看看這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我來到這裏之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會忘記小鬼的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念那時候喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起當時\N我們還偷偷的親熱了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說當時一點也不覺得辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們現在依然在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到沒有人認識的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗通噗通的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一般人的聲音不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們計劃了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人該如何工作賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用存款買車子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人追來了\N就開那輛車逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會先過去等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣，我們約好\N兩個小時後在車站會合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後，我們分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（私大聯考 必考數學II）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶，衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，被宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（緊急出動 大阪遇襲）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大阪受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你立刻出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只有你能拯救民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一仗不打的話\N敵人遲早會攻來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會先過去等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊今天在國中的操場等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我跟你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該也累了吧\N今天就回家去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如往常的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一如往常的走在\N前往學校的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天好像沒發生過什麼事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意放慢腳步\N好讓兩人的距離不要拉遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的好熱喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經秋天了\N還熱得像夏天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我跟你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於上次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的，這個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說，如果你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做了不該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經變成共犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明美啊\N不要嚇人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流\N居然在看我的體育短褲照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少臭美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那副德行\N我才看不上眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，你在看誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼男生總是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛留著這種照片？\N明明都已經是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這種沒談過戀愛的女生\N是不瞭解男生心理的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛突然跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望\N你不要傷千瀨的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛變得這麼嚴肅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨她很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說你最近變得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對她有點疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跑來問我「學姊」是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是你跟冬美學姊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子我在地獄坡\N看到有個人跟她長得很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎著腳踏車擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我們眼睛對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想\N那時候她長得是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情你也要跟千瀨說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的事情一定要跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少囉唆！\N你明明什麼都不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干…幹嘛啦，阿淳\N你不要嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直對她念念不忘，白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子，你在找麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美丟下這句話就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用她多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙搞什麼嘛\N她又不是我媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對她有點疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為我想起冬美學姊的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好要逃到\N沒人認識之處的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果千瀨她沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多事想問她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，為什麼你那天沒有來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不敢問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得不要問比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨一定發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，千瀨，還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩人真的相愛著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，我問你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在鈴聲響起前就知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然大白天就要緊急出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在這麼明顯的地方起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不快點的話，又會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那裏，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那棟房子\N我記得那棟房子是空屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那棟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有輛卡車停在那裏對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁沒人來的時候\N從那裏的後面起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要過來，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會覺得很丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我知道了，我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有人受傷呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼\N只是騎腳踏車跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好像有個女孩跑過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕，怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是修次？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬…冬美學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你長這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國中的時候還是個小不點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些時候碰巧在路上看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想那會不會是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時局真的很不平靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平靜安詳的住宅區\N竟然會突然瓦斯爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老公說\N這一帶應該很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才搬來這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過，真不愧是軍隊駐紮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災害救援總是比人早一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為軍人的妻子\N我覺得很驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是老樣子啊，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一樣沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經念高中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是女生的腳\N臉用不著變得那麼紅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我臉也紅起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱喔，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把窗戶打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣抱在一起\N總感覺好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會對不起我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對不起你的老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿鐵他自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鐵一直沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經快兩個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能躺在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體\N已經不會恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是無法恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我一起逃走的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爽約沒去的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責修理的伯伯說\N已經無法恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇見冬美學姊的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我暫時忘記了千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了她，覺得輕鬆了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是殘酷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:43.46,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.45,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,難以入眠的夜裏總不停的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:59.63,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中黎明已悄悄到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.98,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼想聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:13.15,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,對你的思念越來越強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.09,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,淚水奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:30.26,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:36.50,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍無法忘懷你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.38,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.91,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:52.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬美學姊的事\N真的已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道，我最喜歡的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，明天我們去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終兵器彼女下一回\N「冬美學姊」

